# Todo App Product Spec

## Overview
The Todo App is a web application that allows users to manage their todos, organized by groups and roles.

## Target Users
- Users: individuals who will be using the app to manage their todos
- Admins: users with elevated privileges to manage groups and roles

## Main Features
- User management: registration, login, and profile management
- Group management: create, edit, and delete groups
- Role management: assign roles to users and groups
- Todo management: create, edit, and delete todos
- JWT authentication

## Business Rules
- A user can be part of multiple groups
- A group can have multiple users
- A role can be assigned to multiple users and groups
- Todos are owned by a user and can be shared with groups

## User Stories
- As a user, I want to register and login to the app
- As a user, I want to create and manage my todos
- As an admin, I want to manage groups and roles